## 7. URL Helpers

Use `src/utils/urlHelpers.ts`:

```ts
import { buildAccountRoute, buildMarketplaceRoute } from "../utils/urlHelpers";

buildAccountRoute(accountId, "integrations");      // /brands/1/integrations
buildMarketplaceRoute(accountId, channelId, "google", "campaigns");  // /brands/1/58/google/campaigns
```

