## 9. Create Page Checklist

1. [ ] Create service in `src/services/` if new API
2. [ ] Add query keys in `src/hooks/queries/queryKeys.ts`
3. [ ] Create query/mutation hooks in `src/hooks/queries/` and `src/hooks/mutations/`
4. [ ] Create page in `src/pages/` (or `src/pages/<feature>/`) – use `../../` for imports from subfolders
5. [ ] Use `Sidebar` + `DashboardHeader` (or `AccountsHeader`) + `marginLeft: sidebarWidth`
6. [ ] Call `setPageTitle` / `resetPageTitle` in `useEffect`
7. [ ] Register route in `routes/AccountRoutes.tsx` (or GoogleRoutes, etc.)
8. [ ] Wrap with appropriate route guards
9. [ ] Use design tokens (forest-f40, sandstorm-s0, etc.)
10. [ ] Add link in Sidebar if needed (edit `src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx`)

