## 10. Quick Reference

| Need | Use |
|------|-----|
| Auth user | `useAuth()` from AuthContext |
| Accounts list | `useAccounts()` from AccountsContext |
| Date range | `useDateRange()` from DateRangeContext |
| Sidebar width | `useSidebar().sidebarWidth` |
| API fetch | Service + `useQuery` |
| Create/Update/Delete | Service + `useMutation` |
| Navigation | `useNavigate()`, `useParams()` |
| Design colors | `forest-f40`, `forest-f60`, `sandstorm-s0` |
